metadata.name: "Stray-Dogs" #01-kindly
metadata.description:
"Stray-dogs" is a painting collection that aims to help homeless dogs.
The eerie and disorder in this collection is reminiscent of the situation of defenseless, vulnerable and confused creatures who have been given the name of stray dogs when humans invade the safe area of their lives.

"kindly" is the first piece of this collection.

They can perceive us even from our glance; We cannot have their back, for we lack perceptiveness compared to them.

Mixed Media Painting.
140*100 cm
